Equivalents: ARTH 438
400 Level Art History seminars are restricted to undergraduate and Diploma students. If you are an undergraduate or Diploma student and are unable to register in this class please check to see if the course is full. If this course is full please register in an alternate course or in the waiting list if one is open.
If you are a graduate student seeking to register in this class, please be aware that registration is only permitted by permission of your Faculty Graduate Advisor.
